video.title: Bella and the Bulldogs
video.synopsis: When cheerleader Bella Dawson succeeds in landing a spot on her middle school's football team, her teammates do their best to make her give up.

episodes.synopsis: Middle school cheerleader Bella dreams of playing football, so when the Bulldogs coach lets her try out, she goes for it, no matter what anyone says.
episodes.title: Newbie QB: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Bella passes a scary initiation test that backfires when she can't make an important cheer squad date, then coach kicks her off the team for crying.
episodes.title: Newbie QB: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Bella is starting to feel like part of the team until the guys assume she's been spilling embarrassing secrets to sports reporter Ace McFumbles.
episodes.title: That's Some Gossip, Girl

episodes.synopsis: Bella has to make a tough choice: stay loyal to the team ritual of not showering before the big game or impressing Kyle before her first school dance.
episodes.title: Pretty in Stink

episodes.synopsis: Bella fumbles as the star of Pepper's Tex Fest video. Newt shines when he and Troy try out for the school choir -- until he gets stage fright.
episodes.title: Tex Fest

episodes.synopsis: When Troy has trouble keeping his balance on the field, Bella suggests he attend her mom's ballet class -- and a legendary football star agrees.
episodes.title: Dancing in the End Zone

episodes.synopsis: Sophie and Pepper have a tough time finding a replacement for Bella, but when they do, Bella gets jealous. Troy enlists the guys for a spy mission.
episodes.title: That's My Tri-Five

episodes.synopsis: When Kyle finally asks Bella out on a date, Sophie and Pepper are away, so when he backs out, there’s no one to turn to for advice but the guys.
episodes.title: A Goodbye Week

episodes.synopsis: Bella juggles friendships when Troy and Sawyer compete to be her top receiver and Pepper and Sophie can't get their bake sale together without her.
episodes.title: Bromantically Challenged

episodes.synopsis: A tornado warning ruins Pepper's birthday party after a lockdown keeps the gang at school, but Bella comes up with an idea to get that party started.
episodes.title: Tornado Afraido

episodes.synopsis: Unless Bella can master Spanish, she might have to leave the team. When Newt finds Pepper's list of boys' names, the guys think it's a crush list.
episodes.title: Incomplete Pass

episodes.synopsis: When an injury sidelines Bella from a game, she trains Troy to replace her, then worries it'll be permanent after he scores a winning touchdown.
episodes.title: Backseat Quarterback

episodes.synopsis: Bella's loyalty to the Bulldogs is put to the test when she's asked to the homecoming dance by a player from the Cobras, their biggest rivals.
episodes.title: Traitor Dater

episodes.synopsis: Troy gets jealous when his brother asks Bella to be his mentor. Pepper wants to be Sawyer's girlfriend, even after her parents forbid her to date.
episodes.title: Bulldog Buddies

episodes.synopsis: Bella buries the hatchet with Charlotte after Troy starts dating her, but she may have to change plans when she learns about Charlotte’s secret.
episodes.title: Player Hater

episodes.synopsis: Bella helps Newt get off the bench after half the team gets sick. Troy's latest crush is an older girl, so he needs serious advice from Sophie.
episodes.title: Root for Newt

episodes.synopsis: Bella's overconfidence prompts her to guarantee that the team will make the playoffs, but when they start losing games, she has to change strategies.
episodes.title: Bulldog Blues

episodes.synopsis: When the Bulldogs lose their kicker, Bella suggests a soccer team friend and causes an uproar. Sophie and Pepper try to set up Miss Pepper and Coach.
episodes.title: Kicking and Scheming

episodes.synopsis: Troy urges Bella to ramp up the jokes at the Bulldog's annual roast, but she gets carried away, angering Pepper, Sawyer and most of the team.
episodes.title: Third Degree Ba-Burn

episodes.synopsis: A rival coach unearths an old city rule prohibiting girls from playing football, sending Coach, Bella and the gang into overdrive to change the rules.
episodes.title: No Girls Allowed
